trans-unit.source: Defines the contract for the collection used by ASP.NET session state to manage session.
trans-unit.target: Define o contrato da coleção usada pelo estado de sessão do ASP.NET para gerenciar a sessão.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection> interface defines the collection of session items exposed to application code by the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionStateContainer> class.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection> interface define a coleção de itens de sessão expostos ao código de aplicativo, o <xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionStateContainer> classe.

trans-unit.source: The ASP.NET implementation of the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection> interface is the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection> class.
trans-unit.target: A implementação do ASP.NET do <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection> interface é a <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection> classe.

trans-unit.source: If you create a class derived from the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreProviderBase> class to store session data, you can either use the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection> class to manage the stored objects or implement the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection> interface on your own collection manager.
trans-unit.target: Se você criar uma classe derivada do <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreProviderBase> de classe para armazenar dados de sessão, você pode usar o <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection> classe para gerenciar os objetos armazenados ou implementar o <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection> interface em seu próprio Gerenciador de coleção.

trans-unit.source: If you implement the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection> interface, you must also create a class that inherits the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreProviderBase> class in order to make use of your <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection> implementation to manage session variables.
trans-unit.target: Se você implementar o <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection> interface, você deve criar uma classe que herda de <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreProviderBase> classe para fazer uso de seu <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection> implementação para gerenciar as variáveis de sessão.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection> implementation must also implement the members of the <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> interface.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection> implementação também deve implementar os membros de <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> interface.

trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> Se o <see cref="T:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection" /> conteúdo forem alterados; caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.Dirty%2A> property is used by the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateModule> to determine whether the values in an <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection> implementation have been modified.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.Dirty%2A> propriedade é usada pelo <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateModule> para determinar se os valores em um <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection> implementação foi modificada.

trans-unit.source: In implementing the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection> interface, you should initialize the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.Dirty%2A> property as `false` and set the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Dirty%2A> property to `true` in the implementations of the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.Remove%2A>, <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.RemoveAt%2A>, or <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.Clear%2A> methods.
trans-unit.target: Na implementação o <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection> interface, você deve inicializar o <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.Dirty%2A> a propriedade como `false` e defina o <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Dirty%2A> propriedade `true` em implementações do <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.Remove%2A>, <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.RemoveAt%2A>, ou <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.Clear%2A> métodos.
